beginning, containing an area of SEVENTY NINE THOUSAND ONE HUNDRED NINETY THREE (79,193) SQUARE METERS more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground as B.L. Conc. Mon.; bearing true; date of subdivision survey, July 18, 1960 to January 27, 1961 and approved on April 1, 1964.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 21st day of October, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety-one.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO President of the Philippines

By the President: (Sgd.) FRANKLIN M. DRILON Executive Secretary

